org.vngx.jsch.kex

Class DHGroup14KexAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vngx.jsch.kex.KexAlgorithm
      • org.vngx.jsch.kex.AbstractDHKexAlgorithm
        • org.vngx.jsch.kex.DHGroupKexAlgorithm
          • org.vngx.jsch.kex.DHGroup14KexAlgorithm
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Algorithm

    public final class DHGroup14KexAlgorithm
extends DHGroupKexAlgorithm

    Implementation of KexAlgorithm for "diffie-hellman-group14-sha1" key exchange for SSH. The "diffie-hellman-group1-sha1" method specifies the Diffie-Hellman key exchange with SHA-1 as HASH, and Oakley Group 14 [RFC3526] (2048- bit MODP Group). This method MUST also be supported.

    RFC 4253 - The Secure Shell (SSH) Transport Layer Protocol: 8.2. diffie-hellman-group14-sha1

    RFC 3526 - More Modular Exponential (MODP) Diffie-Hellman groups for Internet Key Exchange (IKE): 2048-bit MODP Group

    Note: The default JCE implementation of Diffie-Hellman does not support key sizes greater than 1024 bits. This implementation must use a security provider (e.g. BouncyCastle) which supports a key size of at least 2048 bits.

    Author:
    Michael Laudati
